Adapt configuration directory for pkgsrc, and avoid touch $HOME during packaging.

--- Makefile.in.orig	2011-01-22 05:36:17.000000000 +0000
+++ Makefile.in
@@ -303,7 +303,7 @@ top_srcdir = @top_srcdir@
